Java 8

Lambda expression provide a clean and concise way to represent a method interface using an expression

Syntax :

     ( Parameters ) -> expression

Or for multiple lines

    ( Parameters )  -> {
      // multiple Statements
    }

Best Use Cases :

1. Functional Interface ( interface with only one abstract method ).
2. Writing short implementations for listeners, comparators, Runnable, etc.
3. Processing collections with Stream API.

